  "text": "Equations (7) and (8) resulting from linearization of the Monge-Ampère equation (2) can be interpreted as gradient flows in measure spaces [CITATION_1] . And thanks to this connection, we can resort to solving a continuity equation characterized by a type of McKean-Vlasov equation, an ODE system that is easier to handle.",
